text: Jaureguina TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in September 2004 and can be seen in the community of La Grita in the Jauregui Municipality of the Tachira State of Venezuela on UHF channel 66. Jesus Avendaño is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
